  "created": "2026-03-21",
  "description": "This preset lives exactly at the Trefoil WEAVE-I threshold — braidDepth 0.38. The LFO on braid depth at 0.08 Hz crosses into topology-dominant territory on each upswing and returns to detuning-dominant territory on each downswing: a 12.5-second cycle of entering and exiting the knot. Below the threshold: rich asymmetric chorus. Above it: the three-strand ring begins to lock, the coupling becomes structural. The WEAVE macro holds the coupling above WEAVE-I permanently. The KNOT macro morphs topology at the threshold. Triangle strands soften the crossing — the topology change is perceptible but not jarring. This preset is a teaching instrument.",
